Settings.QueryText: SELECT CatalogQuestion.Ref FROM Catalog.Question AS CatalogQuestion WHERE CASE WHEN &Owner = UNDEFINED OR &Owner = VALUE(Catalog.QuestionGroup.EmptyRef) THEN TRUE ELSE CatalogQuestion.Owner = &Owner END AND CASE WHEN &Type = UNDEFINED THEN TRUE ELSE CatalogQuestion.Owner.Type = &Type END
SELECT CatalogQuestionGroup.Ref FROM Catalog.QuestionGroup AS CatalogQuestionGroup WHERE CatalogQuestionGroup.Type = &Type
